Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. Have \Nyou ever skated before?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Skating on the ice smoothly,\Nskate and turn... Isn't it so cool?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, I'm making the\Nfirst attempt of my life, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh my! It's super difficult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I'm very good at in-line skating,\NI thought I would be all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I just keep falling\Ndown and running into things,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and it seems I keep saying \Nthings like "Ouch!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, unless I'm able to do this,\NI'm gonna be beat by May.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't back down now, either! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't! I can't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:01:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss hajimari wa \Naka to kuro no Passion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toki ni urahara na kokoro o tayori ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss kirifuda wa mirai o kaeru Mission{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi ni aimai na kotae wa iranai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arienai genjitsu minai furi shite mo Bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egatai shinjitsu\NCan U feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesshiyasui jibun ni Say What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomadou iibun {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' samenai yume ochiteku sadame{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in U hikikae ni subete ushinatte mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who stands on the\Ntop will aim to be a real star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody has reached that top yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real star...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that the hearts of all people\Nwho see that performance will be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even I don't know what\Nkind of performance that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, surpass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And please be a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me you can be a real Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you become a real star,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Kaleido Stage will\Nspread its wings wide again too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla entrusted me with Kaleido Stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I still can't meet her\Nexpectations at all, and yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only that, because of me... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, it means Layla Hamilton\Nwas also a lukewarm performer like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For him to say that about Miss Layla...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, I will work hard in order to be\Nacknowledged by Mr. Leon as his partner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the only thing I can do. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swear one day I'll make him take back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what he said about Miss Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Amazing Match on Ice."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my thoughts, such as\Nthey are, after observing you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I've depressed you, talking about\Nthis at length first thing in the morning, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, were you listening\Nto what I was saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Were you saying something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well... If you're not concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it... might be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have much presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in a sense, that could\Nalso make you a gag character.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to pair with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen May?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she didn't come to the\Nmeeting for the town girls' roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a minor part,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought she'd be all excited because
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's been granted special \Npermission to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, May might not be that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she could be in the middle of\Nspecial training under a mysterious master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she ran away with\Nsomeone tall, dark and handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's not that kind of person either...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I wonder what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a newcomer, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just called him by his first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, all cast members who play\Ntown girls are in the meeting room and--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon, come with me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what I'm \Nlike when I really shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she trying to do this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd show him how\Nshe looks when she really shines...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why ice skating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that May?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, May is good at skating. I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way she skates, she's\Nmore than "good at skating."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ice fairy May Wong is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May's playing the role of\NDracula's leading lady, Mina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if I remember right,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't Mina Murray supposed to\Ndo a Screw Spin using a trapeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:07:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she is good at skating,\Nit has nothing to do with the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true, she's really shining.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the best, May!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, this is how May really shines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia, change the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. How?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dracula will be done on ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On skates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're saying that you're going\Nto choose me as your partner. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me that I should be satisfied\Nwith the way you performed right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What don't you like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The performance I did right now was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be satisfied, but I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't excite me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just like the idea of skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, we're going without\NMina Murray and now he wants it on skates?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is deviating further and\Nfurther from my original image.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Skating... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm going to\Nchallenge you at skating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause in order to play Mina Murray,\NI have to master skating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'll be\Nable to skate better than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I try it, I won't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I want to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she's good at in-line skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be pretty difficult...\NThis could... This could...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her performance level dropped\Nway too much all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to get used to it first...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straighten your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your feet sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh! I'm going to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Keep your back straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike in-line skates, on ice\Nskates you slip less if you slant them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold that pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm skating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you have talent.\NSo I think you'll improve quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Meryl. I work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be from Kaleido Stage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my name is Sora Naegino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you competing with May for a role?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do you know May?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her skating for the first time in\Na while, but her skating is not rusty at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl could shine even on the\Ninternational stage. It's such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine on the international stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When May came to this skating rink,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was only three or four years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I saw her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew May had the talent\Nto compete on the world level.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she kept practicing regularly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought even getting a\Ngold medal could be a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had another dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I want to appear on\Nthe Kaleido Stage with Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her desire was very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I tried to persuade\Nher, she didn't listen to me in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May was that enthralled by Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he saying is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't Leon like me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May told me clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I like skating, but I \Nlike Kaleido Stage more."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be a Kaleido Star,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a real Kaleido Star, like Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm very sorry, Meryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably won't ever wear these shoes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After three years, once\NI finish school, I will audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, one day, I'll definitely stand\Non the same stage as Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, please come to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May's the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been inspired by Miss Layla's\Nperformance on Kaleido Stage like I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, Miss Layla retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she must hate me because I performed\Nthe legendary great maneuver with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to make friends with her,\Nyou have only one way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a bath together immediately, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind not joking like\Nthat when I'm seriously distressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joking? I'm not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously want you, May and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora? I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order not to disappoint May,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to work hard and beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my dad, the rink will\Nbe ready for skating after three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Leon actually skates,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he is supposed to set the \Ncontents of the show in stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So three days from now will be\Ntheir last chance to pass the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In three days?! Don't be rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me to skate in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:14:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to beat May. By all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I have no choice but\Nto ask Meryl to help me after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meryl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meryl is somewhere around the rink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that. Do it stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meryl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you teaching Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want the skill to\Ncompete with you on equal terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May. If you let your guard down,\Nyou will be surpassed by Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surpassed by Sora? {\i1}Me{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is gifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She could be better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the one teaching her, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nonsense! I can't lose at skating.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'll never lose to somebody\Nlike Sora. I will never lose! Never!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, do it more boldly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May's amazing. But I'm sure\NI'm going to catch up with her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For May and for Miss Layla! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora, you have a weakness. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're probably not aware of it, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's so amazing. She's \Nimproving so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She could come from behind and win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is your physical condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I'm in top condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. In that case, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora has a weakness. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she doesn't have enough\Ntime to overcome it in two days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think I should say\Nanything unnecessary right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all finally happens tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Sora can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please let him decide\Nto let Sora play Mina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In only three days, she's gotten this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that possible...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to be accepted by Leon,\Ntechnique itself is not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say Sora's performance is perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's a possibility that she could win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not... I will not let it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not be beaten by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've not seen this kind of\Ndesperation in May for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You're pretty good, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In only three days, what could have changed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The composure she had at\Nthat time is completely gone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of Sora? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Interesting. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be my partner, come up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he jumped over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a superhuman feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Sora be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In terms of the degree\Nof perfection, May is better.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora's performance looks like\Nshe just learned how to skate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When it comes to perfection,\Nit's not worth talking about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She possesses something. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what it is... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I definitely felt it then. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something strange... Something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is it? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will not be beaten by her! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will not lose! Never!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lost. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't be acknowledged by Mr. Leon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, Miss Layla. Sorry, Mia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he pick May?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean May won Leon's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to play Mina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It won't do me any good\Nto keep moping about this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The thing I have to do now is\Nto make Dracula the best show.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Niagara Diving!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can hear it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can hear the applause they're giving us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May, you found a good rival. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Screw Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora, you have a mysterious power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somehow, people around you are\Ninfluenced by you, and start shining.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, in order for you to shine,\Nyou have to overcome your weakness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fight between you two is just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm looking forward to finding out\Nwhich one of you becomes a real star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sekasu you ni muragaru Hard luck{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagasarete Time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yokoku doori Take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:23:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tsuredasu yo imasugu {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gouin only (saisoku drive) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nichijou miorosu best view {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (Stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asu no tame ni escape {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakansu nashi demo oashisu wa get{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keitai off tte ai o charge shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yasashisa dake ja iyasenai itami mo aru kara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are alone. Surechigau{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koukai no hate ni deau true heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naite mo waratte mo I’ll be with U{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:57.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star: New Wings"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.61,0:23:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master Sora, please train me rigorously.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, to my surprise, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rosetta declared to Kalos that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}unless she can master the trapeze \Nin three days, she'll quit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It will be a crash course! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, dear. It seems she caught Sora's disease.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.05,0:24:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But since she's calling me her teacher,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's no choice. I have\Nto do it. I have to! I have to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.95,0:24:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star,\N"Amazing Rosetta of Sweat and Tears."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.63,0:24:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream\Nand on towards the sky...{\i0}
